com.stripe.stripeterminal

Interface ReaderSoftwareUpdateListener


  • public interface ReaderSoftwareUpdateListener
    The ReaderSoftwareUpdateListener handles updates when checking for and installing reader software updates. You must implement the ability to update your reader's software in your app. Though we expect required software updates to be very rare, by using Stripe Terminal, you are obligated to include this functionality. https://stripe.com/docs/terminal/readers/bbpos-chipper2xbt#software-updates-and-releases
